The Proposal:

Reference No. 1 The charitable organization under the Department of Law and Justice was reorganized by a government decision here. However, considering the administrative convenience of the new offices established under the charitable organization during the intervening period, the proposal for re-organization of the charitable organization is referred to Reference No. The government has received letters from 6B7. Accordingly, the matter of restructuring the charitable organization under the Department of Law and Justice was under consideration.
The government's decision:
